{
  "id": "RAW_ace3fc5e",
  "title": "腾讯的这款 AI 产品，让我上头了。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg5Mjc3MjIyMA==&mid=2247579528&idx=1&sn=6328176b33f544a48e44f40374e22177",
  "date": "2026-01-23 12:18:00",
  "author": "阿颖",
  "siteName": "AI产品阿颖",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">腾讯做产品的能力真的强。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">ima 这次更新之后，我觉得终于有一款符合我工作流的 AI 写作工具了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">过去这两年多时间，我用过非常多的 AI 写作工具，包括 Notion、ChatGPT，还有市面上各种大大小小的产品，比如 Writefull、TypeAI。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但坦白讲，都不好用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就拿 ChatGPT 来说，它本质上还是个一问一答的对话助手，不是专门为写作场景设计的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">举个最简单的例子，我写完一篇文章让它帮忙检查错别字，这是它的输出。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100095857\" data-ratio=\"0.2935185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b9305428&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvHicVZXtcAzAHuHEeHQqW21SrFluibc0P3jiczuPHVbh7IcT9Drzu8uWRgCJC0N0qqf76eU2Wup1V9spjlMLgWPhA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我得在文章里，CMD+F，找到对应的错别字后，再挨个修改。用了两年 AI 写作工具，这种破事我干了无数次。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">所以当我发现 ima 的 AI 帮写功能可以直接在原文里批注、一键合并的时候，我的反应是：怎么现在才有人做这个？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">过去我一直把腾讯 ima 当成国产的 NotebookLM 在用，本质上就是一个功能丰富的 AI 知识库。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我经常写文章，写文章就需要素材。所以我的做法是，把自己看过的播客、访谈、公众号文章，全部扔进知识库里。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但我不会偷懒，不会说反正 AI 能帮我记住，那就不看了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不是的，我一定是自己先看一遍，理解了，再放进去。知识库对我来说不是替代大脑，而是扩展大脑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为人脑的容量有限嘛。经常写文章的时候会想起来，诶，马斯克好像说过一句话，挺适合放在这里的，但死活想不起来原话是什么。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">以前的做法是只能去翻原始资料，折腾半天，运气不好还找不到。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">但现在不一样了，我直接问知识库就好，几秒钟的事。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100095858\" data-ratio=\"0.587037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f640ad8c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvHicVZXtcAzAHuHEeHQqW21SrFluibc0P3TypDXZ1h2vUqCCQFm7p1CicWwDDn6qnJJiaw66u0y8ukfMjgfe5Pc6Tg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">这次，它更新了 AI 帮写功能后，我觉得确实是一个非常好的写作类 IDE。可以像 Cursor 一样，提升我们的创作效率。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我下面给大家真刀真枪演示下我是怎么用 ima 创作的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">包括此刻的这篇文章，我也是用 ima 创作。因为 ima 已经是我的第二大脑，加上它的 AI 功能，我在这里写东西效率会高很多。给大家截个图看看。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100095859\" data-ratio=\"0.43425925925925923\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b1c45995&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvHicVZXtcAzAHuHEeHQqW21SrFluibc0P37LvGAo56iciaynkh4qzpo19EicrPrniaZwURDWFwnCxUhd20Klicz0k6vMw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI 帮写功能的按钮在右上角。我感觉这个特性，应该能够帮助更多的人快速完成初稿。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我知道很多人对 AI 创作有一丝芥蒂。特别是在互联网上，有人说这文章是 AI 写的，大家可能就不看了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我觉得没必要这么二极管。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我所有的文章，可以很坦诚地跟大家说，都有 AI 在参与。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但我绝对不会让 AI 帮我直接生成一篇就发了。那种文章里头没有我想表达的东西，完全是别人的创作，本质上就是抄袭或者洗稿，没有意义。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">我的做法是让 AI 参与进来，和我一起完成整个创作过程，让它帮我提升效率。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">作为一个写作者，我非常清楚我们应该利用 AI 的能力来更好地完成工作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">DHH 是圈子里非常知名的程序员，Ruby on Rails 框架的创始人。他前段时间发 X 说，现在已经开始大量使用 AI 写代码了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">虽然仍然会手写，但他承认用 AI 写出来的草稿能够加快研发速度。再早之前，他拒绝使用 AI。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">为了让大家更好的理解 AI 帮写的功能。我完整还原一篇文章的创作过程，这样大家就明白为什么我说 ima 的设计很好了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这两天世界经济论坛达沃斯年会，马斯克分享了他对 AI、太空，还有机器人的判断，非常有料。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我看完了这个视频之后，想写一篇自己的总结文章。之前，2000 字的文章，全部手写的话，即便思路很顺，状态很好，也得 3 个小时，</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">但借助好的工具，我可以一个半小时左右搞定。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &qu